@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At <strong>Classroom Connect</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our platform.
</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Information We Collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> This includes your name, email address, and any other details you provide when creating an account.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with Classroom Connect, such as pages visited, time spent, and actions taken.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Data such as your IP address, browser type, and operating system to help us optimize your experience.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mt-4">How We Use Your Information</h3>
<ul>
    <li>To provide access to and improve our educational services.</li>
    <li>To personalize learning experiences based on your activity and preferences.</li>
    <li>To send relevant updates, announcements, or support information.</li>
    <li>To monitor platform performance and ensure a secure environment for users.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mt-4">Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
<p>
    We do not sell or rent your personal data. Your information may be shared with:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Trusted service providers that help maintain and operate our platform.</li>
    <li>Legal authorities, when required by law or necessary to protect user safety and our rights.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mt-4">Your Rights</h3>
<p>
    You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. You can manage your preferences through your account settings or reach out to our support team.
</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Data Security</h3>
<p>
    We use secure technologies and procedures to safeguard your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Changes to This Policy</h3>
<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy as our services evolve. All changes will be posted on this page along with the revised effective date.
</p>

<h3 class="mt-4">Contact Us</h3>
<p>
    If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy, please contact us at:
    📧 <a href="mailto:support@classroomconnect.com">support@classroomconnect.com</a>
</p>
